<C>__{gittes}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{which one of you is emma dill?}
<A>__{two of them say "she is," and point in different directions. the third gives them a curt look and goes back to her knitting. gittes approaches her.}
<C>__{gittes}
<D>__{are you emma?}
<A>__{some old voice is singing softly, "don't sit under the apple tree."}
<C>__{emma}
<D>__{yes.}
