<D>__{i've been wanting to meet you.}
<C>__{emma}
<D>__{why?}
<C>__{gittes}
<D>__{did you know that you're a very wealthy woman?}
<C>__{emma}
<P>__{(stitching, smiles)}
<D>__{i'm not.}
